    problem: "GDPR fines can reach 4% of annual turnover. 73% of companies still don't fully comply.",
    solution: "We implement a comprehensive compliance program with impact assessments, policies, and procedures.",
    benefits: [
      "Guaranteed regulatory compliance",
      "Reduced sanction risk",
      "Improved customer trust",
